{"tid":1894560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒》武漢市解封 滯留當地外地人士可以出城","createTime":"2020-02-24T04:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T05:39:49.000Z","uid":13663,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"73cb8e69f6a4637acc568bab0d09f99859eec45c","tid":1894560,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"武漢市滯留當地外地人士可以出城<br />\n24.02.2020 11:52<br />\n<br />\n武漢市宣布局部解封，滯留在當地的外地人士，以及因保障疫情防控、城市運行、生產生活、特殊疾病治療等原因必須出城的人士可以出城，但要分批實施及避開高峰時間。當局指，出城人士不可屬於被要求隔離的人士，而且須身體健康，沒有發燒、乾咳、氣喘等症狀，而出城人士到達目的地後，須做好不少過14天的健康監測，並向當地疫情防控指揮部門備案。<br />\n<br />\n至於滯留在外地的武漢市民及車輛，以及因保障疫情防控、城市運行、生產生活、防疫物資運輸等原因必須進城的人士和車輛，按省、市疫情防控指揮部有關規定辦理相關手續後，可以進城。當局在進出城通道設置站點，對出入的車輛和人員，進行檢查，包括核對身份、車輛消毒、體溫檢測、隔離救治、人員防護等工作。"},{"pid":"f8e742d132e5bc76fc410a564fefcd2f114c96ad","tid":1894560,"uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeQhnmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeQhnmP.jpg&h=4bef4f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3Oe81Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3Oe81Q.jpg&h=39571fef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8614ba0e22002009f45ebcba437f32e2953868fc","tid":1894560,"uid":331973,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"香港有2000件落緊來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e036944a4272aae9038a6a99f70a7f4d95b8084e","tid":1894560,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1266530&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAi8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=ae8a8006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266530</a>"}